in_fqfn = _generate_foobarbatz_file(10000, dir_name=self.tmp_dir)
self.cmd = (
    "%(pgm)s %(in_fqfn)s                                   -d ','                                             --fieldcnt 6                                       --quoting 'quote_none'                             --outgood %(outgood)s                              --outerr  %(outerr)s                               --randomout 1.0                              "
     % {'pgm': self.pgm, 'outgood': self.outgood_fqfn, 'outerr': self.
    outerr_fqfn, 'in_fqfn': in_fqfn})
print(self.cmd)
runner = envoy.run(self.cmd)
self.get_outputs(runner)
print(self.std_out)
print(self.std_err)
assert self.status_code == 0
assert not self.err_output
assert len(self.good_output) == 10000
